id: pm-b24b
title: "GH-522: Windows nightly red — init next-steps hints POSIX-quote native Windows paths (quoteCommandArg backslash escaping)"
description: Make init next-step command quoting platform-aware so native Windows paths remain copy-paste-safe in cmd and PowerShell and nightly tests stay green.
