author: maintainer-agent
estimated_minutes: 90
acceptance_criteria: "quoteCommandArg (or a platform-aware wrapper) renders native Windows paths in scoped init hints copy-paste-valid for cmd/PowerShell (no doubled backslashes); the 5 failing specs (4x init-command.spec.ts, 1x init-path-guard.integration.spec.ts) pass on windows-latest Node 24 without weakening the POSIX replacement-sensitive quoting expectations; tests/unit/commands/init-command.spec.ts + tests/integration/init-path-guard.integration.spec.ts pinned into the CI windows-regression suite list (class 8) so this class fails per-PR, not nightly-only; next Nightly Validation windows leg green"
