  "2026-07-12T07:14:29.716Z",maintainer-agent,"Blast radius (2026-07-12 pass): renderPmCommand has 9 call sites across src/cli/{error-guidance,commander-usage,help-json-payload,main,commands/init}.ts — every rendered retry/recovery/usage hint that embeds a native Windows path (e.g. --pm-path values in suggested_retry bundles) ships the same doubled-backslash POSIX escaping, not just init next-steps. The nightly specs only pin the init surface; the fix must land centrally in quoteCommandArg so all surfaces inherit it. Do NOT fix per-call-site."
